 <lb/><del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="StFa" facs="#img_709_z004">East Indian</del> converts <metamark place="inline" function="caret" rend="caret _HMp" change="StFa" facs="#img_709_z005">^</metamark><add place="above" rend="caret _HMp" hand="#HM" change="StFa" facs="#img_709_z006">from lesser isles of the sea</add> may be taken to
